# Book folders — track ONLY the derived digital edition (root .mdx + their *_media/).
# Everything else stays out of git: the Word/PDF sources, the GasunsDhatu_2014 PhD-defense
# dump (~281 MB of PDFs, .xlsm, .rar/.zip, ВАК paperwork) and the Talmud prior-conversion
# scratch (_raw/_pipe .md, chunks/, local notes). Ignore-all-except is used deliberately so
# a stray `git add -A` can never sweep the bulk in; the artifacts are re-included below.
# (gitignore never untracks an already-tracked file, so committed .mdx/_media are safe.)
GasunsDhatu_2014/*
!GasunsDhatu_2014/*.mdx
!GasunsDhatu_2014/*_media/
# H246 print-prep: errata pair + working notes for the 2026 edition (.md — not published by the site)
!GasunsDhatu_2014/errata.yml
!GasunsDhatu_2014/ERRATA.md
!GasunsDhatu_2014/revision-2026/
!GasunsDhatu_2014/CHANGELOG.md
TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/*
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/*.mdx
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/IMPROVEMENT_PLAN.md
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/student-roadmap.md
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/visual-grammar.md
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/talmud-refactoring.md
# H915 Zaliznyak on-ramp: design docs + the whole onramp/ subfolder (mdx + _category_)
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/ZALIZNYAK_ONRAMP_DESIGN.md
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/ZALIZNYAK_ONRAMP_DESIGN.meta.md
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/onramp/
# H242 scaffold: errata pair, session journal, human-gated footnote proposals
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/errata.yml
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/ERRATA.md
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/.ai_state.md
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/footnote-proposals/
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/CHANGELOG.md
# ApteSyntax_1885 — the root Apte-unicode.mdx is already tracked; the unpacked
# archive under src/ carries the derived .mdx (+ Pandoc-extracted *_media/) we
# also want, but its Word/PDF/RTF/HTML/JPG/.dat/.txt sources and the 101 MB
# 01_Apte.zip (over GitHub's 100 MB file limit) must stay out of git.
ApteSyntax_1885/01_Apte.zip
ApteSyntax_1885/src/**
!ApteSyntax_1885/src/**/
!ApteSyntax_1885/src/**/*.mdx
!ApteSyntax_1885/src/**/*_media/**
# H241 Phase-3 enrichment crosswalk: derived data asset + reproducible generators
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/data/
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/tools/
# H329: raw /z/ scrape cache stays local (guardrail — commit only the derived join map)
TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/data/raw_cache/
# H411: Tolchelnikov's companion papers/talks (papers/) — same derived-edition-only
# policy as the book itself: track only the converted .mdx + extracted media, plus
# the two PDFs that are themselves the only source (Desnickaya_2020/Kulikov_2025 have
# no .docx to convert). Docx/pptx/extra-PDF sources in the other paper folders stay out.
# (Explicit per-subfolder negation, not a recursive **-glob: git won't re-include a
# file via a later `!**/*.mdx` once an ancestor directory itself was excluded by an
# earlier rule — verified this the hard way, `**/` directory negation silently no-ops.)
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/index.mdx
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/_category_.json
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/Auroville_Feb2024/
TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/Auroville_Feb2024/*
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/Auroville_Feb2024/*.mdx
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/Auroville_Feb2024/_category_.json
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/Auroville_Feb2024/*_media/
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/Auroville_Feb2024/*_media/**
!TolchelnikovTalmud_2026/papers/Dubyanskiye_2024/
